title: Dell PowerVault ME5: Controller Health
agents: dell_powervault_me5
catalog: hw/storagehw/dell
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors each storage controller of a Dell PowerVault ME5 system: health,
 operational status, fail-over state, cache write policy and redundancy. The
 model, cache size and port/disk counts are shown for reference.

 State is taken from the controller health value reported by the array. The
 mapping of each condition is configurable via the "Dell PowerVault ME5
 controller health" ruleset.

item:
 The controller id (for example {"A"} or {"B"}).

discovery:
 One service is created per controller.
